  m_text: Survive against hordes of Unholy creatures by slaying them and picking
    up rewards (when they drop). You must increase your multiplier as high as you
    can by consistently damaging enemies before it drops. The higher the multiplier
    the better the weapons, and the better the drops will be. You can heal by picking
    up specific drops, although be careful trying to run into hordes. Some enemy
    units have high armour and only take damage from specific heavy penetration weapons.
    Good luck, and beware the demons...
